BlastDown - Space Invaders
=========================

## Overview
Summer 2014 [Rally Software](http://www.rallydev.com/) Project.  This project aims to create a fun way to interact with and view the Rally data model.  Check out our early vision for the project:

![Space Invaders graphics](http://s11.postimg.org/422x7xkkj/blastdown.png)
